com.mapbox.vision.visionevents.events.detection

Class Detections

  • com.mapbox.vision.visionevents.events.detection.Detections

  • public class Detections

    Holds detections with sourceImage they were made from.

    IMPORTANT : do not cache sourceImage. Data that it holds can be invalidated. Instead, if you need the data, call Image.getImageBitmap or Image.getImageBytes and handle it.

    See Also:
    Image.getImageBitmap, Image.getImageBytes
